    <p>Purchases in this category fall under the invitational procurement category, which means you’re required to request vendor proposals for your good or service. As negotiations for specific requirements such as delivery, warranties or terms and conditions are often involved in this spend threshold, you may wish to request assistance from <a href="/content/ryerson/financial-services/contact/purchasing-payment.html">Purchasing Services</a>.</p> 
